; Regression test for issue #587: ledger --anon print regex fails (BZ#587)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/587
;
; The bug reported that using --anon with the print command and a regex filter
; would fail (crash or incorrect behavior). This test verifies that --anon print
; correctly applies regex filtering without crashing.
;
; The --anon flag anonymizes payee names and account names using hashed values,
; so the test uses a non-matching regex which produces deterministic empty output.

2024/01/01 Payee
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/02 Other Payee
    Expenses:Books   $20.00
    Assets:Cash

; Test that --anon print with a non-matching regex produces empty output
; (this is deterministic regardless of the random hashes used by --anon)
test --anon print NoSuchAccount
end test
